<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <title>Subscription Upgraded</title>
    <style>
        body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; line-height: 1.6; color: #333; }
        .container { max-width: 600px; margin: 0 auto; padding: 20px; }
        .header { background: #10B981; color: white; padding: 30px; text-align: center; border-radius: 8px 8px 0 0; }
        .content { background: #f9fafb; padding: 30px; border-radius: 0 0 8px 8px; }
        .button { display: inline-block; background: #10B981; color: white; padding: 12px 24px; text-decoration: none; border-radius: 6px; margin: 20px 0; }
        .footer { text-align: center; margin-top: 30px; color: #6b7280; font-size: 14px; }
        .feature-list { background: white; padding: 20px; border-radius: 8px; border: 1px solid #e5e7eb; margin: 20px 0; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <div class="container">
        <div class="header">
            <h1>🚀 Plan Upgraded!</h1>
        </div>
        <div class="content">
            <h2>Hello {{name}}!</h2>
            <p>Great news! Your NotifyX account has been successfully upgraded to the <strong>{{plan}}</strong> plan.</p>
            
            <p>You now have access to premium features:</p>
            <div class="feature-list">
                <ul>
                    {{#each features}}
                    <li>{{this}}</li>
                    {{/each}}
                </ul>
            </div>
            
            <p>Start exploring your new features now!</p>
            
            <a href="{{frontendUrl}}/dashboard" class="button">Go to Dashboard</a>
            
            <p>Thank you for choosing NotifyX for your career growth!</p>
            
            <p>Best regards,<br><strong>The NotifyX Team</strong></p>
        </div>
        <div class="footer">
            <p>© 2024 NotifyX. All rights reserved.</p>
        </div>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
